ns have uncovered various relics in and around Pyongyang.”<ref>{{Cite book|language=ja|author={{ill|Sadayoshi Sekino|ja|関野貞|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sadayoshi Sekino|qq=}}|date=1914|title=The Ruins of the Lelang-Daebang Period in Korea|series=Anthropological Magazine 29 (10)|publisher={{ill|Japanese Society of Anthropology|ja|日本人類学会|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Society of Anthropology|qq=}}|page=379}}</ref>
